om\": 2108, \"to\": 2132}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Russia's Prosecutor General's Office has designated The Moscow Times as an \\\"undesirable\\\" organization, criminalizing our work and putting our staff at risk of prosecution.\", \"from\": 2136, \"to\": 2307, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2136, \"end\": 2142, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999711174731286, \"rank\": 2.820069296418069e-05, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 2145, \"end\": 2163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prosecutor-General_of_Russia\", \"score\": 0.9985002583441593, \"rank\": 0.0015019942294582766, \"text\": \"Prosecutor General\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prosecutor-General_of_Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prosecutor-General_of_Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 2188, \"end\": 2204, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Moscow_Times\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Moscow Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Moscow_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Moscow_Times\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an \\\"undesirable\\\" organization\", \"from\": 2208, \"to\": 2237}, {\"ngram\": \"our work\", \"from\": 2253, \"to\": 2261}, {\"ngram\": \"our staff\", \"from\": 2274, \"to\": 2283}, {\"ngram\": \"risk\", \"from\": 2287, \"to\": 2291}, {\"ngram\": \"prosecution\", \"from\": 2295, \"to\": 2306}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This follows our earlier unjust labeling as a \\\"foreign agent.\\\"\", \"from\": 2308, \"to\": 2370, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our earlier unjust labeling\", \"from\": 2321, \"to\": 2348}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"foreign agent\", \"from\": 2352, \"to\": 2368}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These actions are direct attempts to silence independent jour